{"tid":1917203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"士可殺 不可辱","createTime":"2020-03-09T10:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T14:55:31.000Z","uid":114951,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea04521a58129e58841c4727c01256566ba8c09b","tid":1917203,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:54:33.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n個位手足<br />\n辛苦你，你已經比好多鍵戰勇敢<br />\nreally respect<br />\n第二<br />\n我明大家面對黑警可能會好驚<br />\n我都試過<br />\n但係希望大家搵番堆火出黎<br />\n<strong>唔好屈服係黑警嘅屈辱底下</strong><br />\n你要記住<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你冇做錯<br />\n錯嘅係班狗</span></span></strong><br />\n你可以選擇唔講野<br />\n有本事可以同佢理論<br />\n仲有好多其他野可以做<br />\n最後<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家見到咁嘅事發生<br />\n咁都吞得落呢啖氣?<br />\n一齊加油，爭氣<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"97274746d948ad4b7088ecdf7b3c7d015d15a7a6","tid":1917203,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"c2c96ee721dcbe737e304aa53232535bdc25d8a3","tid":1917203,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:55:14.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"2d7be2a2aea70616b572e81b00c545cd2511c743","tid":1917203,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"70509c6a23302d50aa2ed31604126a0feb0beaa0","tid":1917203,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:55:41.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"fa22b23c45e5664837e2ceaf5e3ee097da7e6a74","tid":1917203,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"97ea465396cb57b5b6eb814de37fcf171f561ea5","tid":1917203,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"4c4b0f6edf93f0feb4fb7abe879fa4f83d0531a7","tid":1917203,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"